SUBJECT: Your Job Application: Next Steps
CONTENT: Greetings applicant, We have reviewed your application and we are excited to let you know that we find your profile interesting.  The selection process goes this way: 1. Assessment 2. Short Phone Interview 3. Onboarding  For the assessment, you will be required to write an article of your choice from the list of topics we provide. Onsubmitting it, one of our editors will review it and you will get to know if it's approved or rejected through us within 2-3 days. Let's begin with the assessment.  I am Nancy Pawar from the HR Team. I will provide a link and in there:  1. You will have to fill out a google form in which you will have to select a topic to write your assessment article on.  2. Then you will have to write the article and submit it in the submission link that is there below in the same link before.   Deadline:  Date- 8th June,2022 Time- 2 p.m.  Link: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sqy9pW3FHJEgvOUTT58ZhBWVm-ejPXj3RcVGgSqYooM/edit?usp=sharing  Kindly go to the link and pick a topic from the first form, draft your article and upload it in the second link given in the link itself.  Please note: 1.Check for the auto-generated mail after submitting the first form (selection of the topic)  2.Please write a plagiarism-free article, articles with plagiarism of more than 12% get REJECTED immediately.Please check the plagiarism of your article on Quetext. Link: https://www.quetext.com/plagiarism-checker   3.Make sure you reach the word count that is mentioned in front of the topic name. Kindly follow all of the instructions on article structure given in the link.  4.If your assessment article gets selected you will be paid for it at the end of the month.  5.Please mention my name (Nancy Pawar) in the space for "HR name and number" while filling the submission form.  Feel free to ask questions and if any of this is not clear,we can have a one to one call before the assessment and interview as well.  Good luck!  HR Nancy Pawar College Aftermath Content Writing Internship

The Plaksha University is your kind of place.

We invite you to join us on this transformative journey that will redefine your career path.
